<html>
    <head>
        <title>Metadata.Exposed</title>
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
          integrity="sha256-3edrmyuQ0w65f8gfBsqowzjJe2iM6n0nKciPUp8y+7E="
          crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src='https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js'></script>
        <script>
        $('#file_form').keydown(function() {
          var key = e.which;
          if (key == 13) {
            // As ASCII code for ENTER key is "13"
            $('#file_form').submit(); // Submit form code
            }
          });
        </script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Metadata Exposed!</h1>
        <p>This service is provided for free for digital investigators.</p>
        <p>For your protection, files are deleted immediately after parsing. If you do not wish to upload your files, you may run <a href="https://github.com/jcran/galton">this service</a> locally.</p>
        <p>
        <form id="file_form" action="/save" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <input type="file" name="file"/><br/><br/>
            <%= "#{recaptcha_tags if settings.environment == :production}" %>
            <input type="submit"/>
        </form>
        </p>
        <p>Metadata parsing powered by: <a href="https://tika.apache.org/1.17/formats.html">Apache Tika</a><p>
    </body>
</html>
